def print_word_pos_sentence(word_sentence, pos_sentence):
    assert len(word_sentence) == len(pos_sentence)
    for word, pos in zip(word_sentence, pos_sentence):
        print(f"{word}({pos})", end="\u3000")
    print()
    return
    
for i, sentence in enumerate(sentence_list):
    print()
    print(f"'{sentence}'")

測試：篩選特定詞性作為 stop word 刪除¶

In [36]:
without_stopword = []
def text_without_stopword(word_sentence, pos_sentence):
    assert len(word_sentence) == len(pos_sentence)
    for word, pos in zip(word_sentence, pos_sentence):
        # stop word 
        if pos != 'Caa' and pos != 'Cab' and pos != 'Cba' and pos != 'Cbb' and pos != 'D' and pos != 'Da' and pos != 'Dfa' and pos != 'Di' and pos != 'DE' and pos != 'Nd' and pos != 'Nep' and pos != 'Nes' and pos != 'Neu' and pos != 'Nf' and pos != 'Ng' and pos != 'Nh' and pos != 'P' and pos != 'T' and pos != 'VG' and pos != 'VF' and pos != 'SHI' and pos != 'V_2' and pos != 'COLONCATEGORY' and pos != 'COMMACATEGORY' and pos != 'DASHCATEGORY' and pos != 'ETCCATEGORY' and pos != 'EXCLAMATIONCATEGORY' and pos != 'PARENTHESISCATEGORY' and pos != 'PAUSECATEGORY' and pos != 'PERIODCATEGORY' and pos != 'QUESTIONCATEGORY' and pos != 'SEMICOLONCATEGORY' and pos != 'SPCHANGECATEGORY' and pos != 'WHITESPACE': 
            without_stopword.append(word)
            print(f"{word}({pos})", end="\u3000")
    return

for i, sentence in enumerate(sentence_list):
    text_without_stopword(word_sentence_list[i],  pos_sentence_list[i])

print()

建立函式¶

In [37]:
def all_text_without_stopword(sentence_list):
    word_sentence_list = ws(sentence_list)
    pos_sentence_list = pos(word_sentence_list)
    without_stopword = []
    for i, sentence in enumerate(sentence_list):
        assert len(word_sentence_list[i]) == len(pos_sentence_list[i])
        for word, POS in zip(word_sentence_list[i], pos_sentence_list[i]):
            # stop word 
            if POS != 'Caa' and POS != 'Cab' and POS != 'Cba' and POS != 'Cbb' and POS != 'D' and POS != 'Da' and POS != 'Dfa' and POS != 'Di' and POS != 'DE' and POS != 'Nd' and POS != 'Nep' and POS != 'Nes' and POS != 'Neu' and POS != 'Nf' and POS != 'Ng' and POS != 'Nh' and POS != 'P' and POS != 'T' and POS != 'VG' and POS != 'VF' and POS != 'SHI' and POS != 'V_2' and POS != 'COLONCATEGORY' and POS != 'COMMACATEGORY' and POS != 'DASHCATEGORY' and POS != 'ETCCATEGORY' and POS != 'EXCLAMATIONCATEGORY' and POS != 'PARENTHESISCATEGORY' and POS != 'PAUSECATEGORY' and POS != 'PERIODCATEGORY' and POS != 'QUESTIONCATEGORY' and POS != 'SEMICOLONCATEGORY' and POS != 'SPCHANGECATEGORY' and POS != 'WHITESPACE': 
                without_stopword.append(word)
    return without_stopword

all_text_without_stopword(sentence_list)
